<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,288,730,754]" pageId="19" pageNumber="194">FIGURE 12.</emphasis>
Male genitalia of 
<taxonomicName box="[477,642,730,754]" class="Insecta" family="Rutelidae" genus="Anomala" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="194" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="undefined-A">
